extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #[em Supplies Store], a very basic Express website developed as an assignment project for The Odin Project curriculum.

  h2 Dynamic Store Status

  if error
    p Error getting the store data.
  else
    p Store has the following record counts:

    ul
      li #[strong Items:] !{data.item_count}
      li #[strong Categories:] !{data.category_count}
